                <h1>Exploring the Legacy of MF DOOM: A Hip-Hop Icon</h1>
                <p>MF DOOM, known for his complex wordplay and unique production style, remains a pillar in the underground hip-hop scene. With his iconic metal mask and mysterious persona, he crafted timeless tracks that blended comic book references with introspective lyrics. His influence is felt across genres, inspiring countless artists even after his passing.</p>
